      • RouteSelectorEvaluation

        public RouteSelectorEvaluation(boolean succeeded,
                               double quality,
                               io.ktor.util.ValuesMap values,
                               int segmentIncrement)

        Represents a result of a route evaluation against a call

        参数:
        succeeded - indicates if a route matches current class RoutingResolveContext
        quality - indicates quality of this route as compared to other sibling routes
        values - is an instance of ValuesMap with parameters filled by class RouteSelector
        segmentIncrement - is a value indicating how many path segments has been consumed by a selector
